    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sticky Mayhem is a rogue-like action game where you can build human towers &amp; can battle with each other. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft your human tower by understanding the physics &amp; balance of human tower building. Pick the right soldiers, armor, weapon, engines, etc. for combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In battle, use speed, shape of the tower and your weapons to attack and destroy your opponent.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After every round use the earnings to upgrade your soldiers, armor, weapon, engines, etc. for the next forthcoming rounds.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Sandbox mode to experiment on pyramid structure, combination of soldiers &amp; weapons.</p>",
